<b>First...</b>

02:44.050 --> 02:44.850
<b>Oh?</b>

02:46.520 --> 02:50.660
<b>Now that I get a closer look, 
you're pretty cute, Akame.</b>

02:50.660 --> 02:52.400
<b>Where'd that come from?</b>

02:52.830 --> 02:54.620
<b>I'm Chelsea.</b>

02:54.620 --> 02:57.150
<b>Let's all get along as fellow assassins, okay?</b>

02:57.570 --> 02:58.780
<b>Here, have a treat.</b>

03:00.670 --> 03:02.120
<b>Welcome aboard.</b>

03:02.120 --> 03:04.340
<b>Whoa! She won Akame over with sweets!</b>

03:04.340 --> 03:06.790
<b>She must have been hungry from the long trip.</b>

03:07.170 --> 03:12.020
<b>Chelsea looks even less like an assassin than Mine and the rest, though.</b>

03:12.020 --> 03:13.500
<b>Don't judge a book by its cover.</b>

03:14.070 --> 03:17.800
<b>She's incredibly talented, and she's already made around as many kills as Akame.</b>

03:17.800 --> 03:18.630
<b>What?{Eh?}{Not a fan of "eh" in this instance}</b>

03:19.170 --> 03:25.100
<b>And here's my new Imperial Relic, 
courtesy of the Revolutionary Army:</b>

03:25.100 --> 03:27.430
<b>The Lightning-Speed Warrior, Susanoo.</b>

03:27.430 --> 03:31.060
<b>He's an autonomous living Relic, 
so he's easy to handle.</b>

03:31.570 --> 03:33.960
<b>In other words, even I can use him.</b>

03:33.960 --> 03:35.900
<b>N-Nice to meet you again.</b>

03:38.910 --> 03:40.180
<b>Wh-What?</b>

03:42.910 --> 03:43.910
<b>There.</b>

03:44.470 --> 03:46.960
<b>He's a real neat freak, surprisingly enough.</b>

03:46.960 --> 03:48.700
<b>First time I've seen a Relic like that.</b>

03:49.700 --> 03:52.460
<b>Actually, he also fixed my hair, didn't he?</b>

03:52.460 --> 03:56.040
<b>So what's his power?</b>

03:56.040 --> 03:57.710
<b>Is he just physically strong, or what?</b>

04:00.720 --> 04:02.680
<b>Allow us to demonstrate.</b>

04:02.680 --> 04:03.930
